result.reason: The ~15-20 simultaneous RDP connection limit is a Windows Server-side restriction governed by RDP licensing (CALs) and Group Policy, not an mRemoteNG client-side limitation.
result.approach: Server-side limit — users need to configure RDP session limits via Group Policy (tsconfig.msc) or acquire additional RDS CALs; no client-side fix in mRemoteNG.
